<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent5beccc8559d54107bb7dfde9cb4732cd">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Teesside's newest hospital, Tees Valley Hospital" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=189620"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>Tees Valley Treatment Centre has been delivering NHS services for ten years and has established a reputation with patients and the healthcare community for consultant led services and high patient satisfaction.</p>
<p>Tees Valley Treatment Centre has now moved to a brand new facility - Tees Valley Hospital which is situated on Church Lane, on the grounds of Acklam Hall in Middlesbrough.</p>
<p>The hospital offers a wide range of treatments and services across an array of departments.</p>
<ul>
<li>Dermatology</li>
<li>Endoscopy</li>
<li>Oral &amp; maxillofacial      surgery</li>
<li>Orthopaedic surgery</li>
<li>Plastic surgery</li>
<li>General surgery</li>
<li>Podiatric surgery</li>
<li>Urology</li>
</ul>
<p>Please click the <a href="/Services/hospitals/Services/DefaultView.aspx?id=411" target="_self" title="Choose and book services">departments and services</a> for treatments available on Choose and Book.</p>
<p>Registered with the Care Quality Commission patients can be assured of the highest standards in surgical, nursing, hygiene and aftercare services at Tees Valley Hospital.</p>
<p>The endoscopy service has recently achieved Joint Advisory Group accreditation an industry standard for the delivery of endoscopy procedures so patients can be assured they will receive the highest quality of clinical care and patient experience.</p>
<p>All appointments, procedures, surgery and aftercare take place at Tees Valley Hospital and patients can be assured of a warm welcome.</p>
<p><strong>Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Three laminar flow theatres</li>
<li>Dedicated endoscopy suite</li>
<li>Overnight en-suite      bedrooms</li>
<li>12 day patient pods</li>
<li>X-ray &amp; ultrasound      facilities</li>
<li>Mobile MRI &amp; CT</li>
<li>Physiotherapy unit &amp;      rehabilitation gym</li>
<li>100 free on-site parking      spaces</li>
</ul>
<p>The hospital is within easy reach of A19 and a 15 minute taxi ride from Middlesbrough Train Station.</p>
