<div class="pad clear">
<h4 id="Article-177119">Tees Valley Hospital: New hospital opens its doors to the Teesside community  </h4>
<div id="imageContent87872f2110854a81a55ce13c50a08df9">
</div>
<p>Tees Valley Treatment Centre which was based in the One Life Building in Middlesbrough has now moved to Tees Valley Hospital situated on the grounds of Acklam Hall in Middlesbrough.</p>
<p class="Default">Teesside’s newest private hospital situated on the door step of the Tees Valley community provides surgical, medical and assessment services to NHS, self-pay and insured patients. </p>
<p class="Default">For more information on how to access healthcare at Tees Valley Hospital please visit: <a href="http://www.teesvalleyhospital.co.uk/patients/accessing-healthcare" title="Accessing Healthcare at Tees Valley Hospital">www.teesvalleyhospital.co.uk/patients/accessing-healthcare</a></p>
<p class="last-updated">Last updated on 14 March 2018.</p>
